snippet.title: Math Blaster for 5th Grade - Part 1: Intoduction & Enlightening up the Dining Room
snippet.description:
Math Blaster for 5th Grade
Part 1: Introduction & Enlightening up the Dining Room

Math Skills are Disappearing! There's an electrochemical Math Magnet located in the Bizzaroville Haunted House, which is turning citizens into Mathematical Zombies! Here Rave must stop Dr. Dabble, who is responsible for all this mess. Rave must go find the fuses and install the fuses into the fusebox in the Library and get to Dr. Dabble's secret lab to derail the Math Magnet and save Bizzaroville!
